This paper is about deep learning and incorporating human knowledge into the modeling process. It focuses on model attributions and priors, which are important topics in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
